{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@MLNOfflinePackProgress"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The progress of an inactive or completed pack is computed lazily, and all its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"fields are set to 0 by default. To request the pack’s progress, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"-requestProgress","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method. To get notified when the progress becomes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"known and when it changes, observe KVO change notifications on this pack’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"state","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" key path. Alternatively, you can add an observer for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"s about this pack that come from the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"default notification center.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"The pack’s current progress.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(py)progress","roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"}],"title":"progress","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"}]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/progress":{"abstract":[{"text":"The pack’s current progress.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"progress","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgress":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A structure containing information about an offline pack’s current download"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"progress."}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogress","title":"MLNOfflinePackProgress"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflineStorage"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","title":"MLNOfflineStorage"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification":{"title":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogresschangednotification","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Posted by the shared "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"},{"type":"text","text":" object when an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object’s progress changes. The progress may change due to a resource being"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"downloaded or because the pack discovers during the download that more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"resources are required for offline viewing. This notification is posted"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"whenever any field in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"progress"},{"type":"text","text":" property changes."}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","type":"topic","title":"MLNOfflinePack","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePack","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},{"type":"text","text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a region offline to a local database."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","role":"symbol"}}}